data.description: Captivating 2-story baby Georgian home awaits its new owner. This charming residence features 2 spacious bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, ample storage, an inviting eat-in kitchen, and a separate dining room. Enjoy the comfort of new central air conditioning and a recent upgrade to a 220 AMP electrical service. The kitchen, renovated less than 5 years ago, boasts modern appliances, including a refrigerator and stove installed approximately 8 months ago, and a microwave that's around 1 year old. The new bathrooms, completed just a month ago, add a touch of contemporary elegance. Additional features include ceiling fans and meticulous workmanship throughout. 2 car garage with shade overhang in this very spacious backyard. Owner says the neighbors are the best.  Conveniently located facing the Eisenhower Expressway, this home provides easy access for a seamless commute. Don't miss the chance to own this adorable home - it won't be on the market for long."
